ImageAsset - Class in com.ezrebclan.asset.assetTypes
An ImageAsset holds a BufferedImage as its data.
ImageAssets also includes extra data in its AssetIndex: X Resolution (Width) Y Resolution (Hieght) Full Resolution (WidthxHieght)
ImageAsset(String, BufferedImage) - Constructor for class com.ezrebclan.asset.assetTypes.ImageAsset
Creates an ImageAsset, assigns it a name, and stores the image in the data field.
ImageAsset(InputStream) - Constructor for class com.ezrebclan.asset.assetTypes.ImageAsset
Loads an ImageAsset from an InputStream
index - Variable in class com.ezrebclan.asset.core.Asset
An index object that holds info about the data.
